# React Adapter Rules

## Purpose
This package bridges kata-core (Headless) to React.

## Tech Stack
React 19, Hooks, Context API.

## Constraints

- Must NOT contain game logic. All logic belongs in kata-core.
- Must only render data based on KSONFrame.
- Use useEffect to subscribe to engine.on('update').

## Naming
Hooks must start with use. Components must be functional.
